            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Subscription and billing systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Customer portals and dashboards</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Marketplace and two-sided platforms</span>
