          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Enterprise Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Complex, multi-system implementations for organizations operating at scale.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Cross-department platforms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Legacy system modernization</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">•</span>
              <span>Enterprise data layers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
