            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Define the Product</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We start with what you're building—the problem it solves, who it's for, and what success looks like.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 italic">
              No assumptions. No templates. Just clarity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 02 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            02
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Design & Architect</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
