          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Build in Iterations</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We build in weekly cycles with visible progress. Working software, not slide decks.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 italic">
              Short loops. Fast feedback. No surprises.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 04 -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
            04
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Deploy & Hand Off</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              We deploy to your infrastructure, document everything, and hand off complete ownership.
